    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>Your attacks are so powerful, they can flatten your opponents. When you use @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.pVLdMOqYwul745k3]{Knockback}, you can attempt an @Check[type:athletics|defense:fortitude] check against your target's Fortitude DC.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> You gain the critical success effect of a @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.7blmbDrQFNfdT731]{Shove}, then the critical success effect of a @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.ge56Lu1xXVFYUnLP]{Trip} against the target.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> You gain the success effect of a Shove, then the success effect of a Trip against the target.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> You gain the normal effect of Knockback.</p>"
